    {
        "content": "<p><span aria-label=\"exclamation\" class=\"emoji emoji-2757\" role=\"img\" title=\"exclamation\">:exclamation:</span> unknown identifier 'integral_mono'<br>\nDid you mean <a href=\"https://loogle.lean-lang.org/?q=%22integral_mono%22\"><code>\"integral_mono\"</code></a>, <a href=\"https://loogle.lean-lang.org/?q=MeasureTheory.integral_mono\"><code>MeasureTheory.integral_mono</code></a>, or <a href=\"https://loogle.lean-lang.org/?q=integral_mono\">something else</a>?</p>",
